---
source: crates/kul-wasm/tests/format.rs
expression: formatted
---
# Adoption, and where a person belongs.
#
# The Mendoza household is built mostly by adoption. Carlos and Rosa
# have one biological child, Mateo, and they adopt two more: Dalisay and
# Bayani. In Kul, adopted and biological children are equal members of
# the family — the only difference a reader sees is the connector style:
# a biological link draws a solid edge, an adoption a dashed one.
#
# A person can carry several family ties at once — a `birth` and one or
# more `adoption`s. Only one of them is *current*, chosen by a simple
# priority: a current marriage first, else the most recent adoption, else
# the birth family, else the person stands alone. Dalisay shows the full
# chain: born to one couple, adopted by another whose adoption later
# ended, and finally adopted by Carlos and Rosa. Her canonical card lives
# with the Mendozas (her current family); each earlier tie stays in the
# data and surfaces a faded child-ghost where it would have sat — a solid
# one at her birth family, a dashed one at the earlier adoption.
#
# `gender:` takes `male`, `female`, or `other`, and is never drawn as a
# shape or colour — Bayani's `gender:other` is just a label like any
# name field.

# ---- The Mendozas ----
person carlos  name:"Carlos Mendoza"  gender:male    born:1973-02-18
person rosa    name:"Rosa Mendoza"    gender:female  born:1975-09-24

marriage m_carlos_rosa carlos rosa  start:2000-01-15

# Mateo — biological child (solid edge).
person mateo  name:"Mateo Mendoza"  gender:male  born:2003-05-10
  birth m_carlos_rosa

# Bayani — adopted, no birth family on record; the Mendozas are the only
# (and therefore current) family.
person bayani  name:"Bayani Mendoza"  gender:other  born:~1995
  adoption m_carlos_rosa  start:2007-06-01

# Dalisay — born to one couple, adopted by another, then by the Mendozas.
person dalisay  name:"Dalisay Mendoza"  gender:female  born:1990-08-03
  birth m_eduardo_luz
  adoption m_tomas_elena  start:1994-04-20  end:1999-02-10
  adoption m_carlos_rosa  start:2002-11-30

# ---- Dalisay's birth family ----
person eduardo  name:"Eduardo Reyes"  gender:male    born:1962-03-11
person luz      name:"Luz Reyes"      gender:female  born:1965-12-02

marriage m_eduardo_luz eduardo luz  start:1988-07-09

# ---- Dalisay's earlier (ended) adoptive family ----
person tomas  name:"Tomas Garcia"  gender:male    born:1958-06-25
person elena  name:"Elena Garcia"  gender:female  born:1960-10-14

marriage m_tomas_elena tomas elena  start:1985-03-01
